label.value: Azaribine

value.value: The triacetate salt of azauridine, a synthetic triazine nucleoside derivative possessing antineoplastic and anti-psoriatic activity. After metabolism to 6-azauridine-5-prime monophosphate, 6-Azauridine inhibits de novo pyrimidine biosynthesis and its 5-prime triphosphate metabolite gets incorporated into RNA, thereby preventing RNA synthesis.

label.value: Biological Grandchild

value.value: A biological child of an individual's biological child.

label.value: Biological Grandparent

value.value: A biological parent of the biological father or biological mother.

label.value: Biological Child

value.value: A son or daughter with genetic makeup inherited from the parent.

label.value: Third Degree Relative

value.value: Any individual related biologically or legally to another individual and considered two degrees removed from the immediate family as in the case of cousins.

label.value: Biological Sibling

value.value: A person's brother or sister with whom they share a genetic makeup inherited from one or both of their shared biological parents.
